Mass Heal wipes away disease and injury from all living allies in the area of effect. It cures blindness, diseases, feeblemind and restores the targets to maximum hit points if they have been injured. Enemy undead in the area of effect suffer the effects of a Harm spell if the caster succeeds on a ranged touch attack roll for each one.~
